nodes.text: Green Five was the call sign of the fifth member of Green Squadron. There were a number of starfighter squadrons with this name, and several pilots went by the call sign Green Five.
Habeer Zignean used the call sign during the evacuation of Hoth.
After the Battle of Hoth, Olin Garn flew an X-wing as Green Five in the Battle of Hospital.
Years later, Kell Tainer flew as Green Five during his training period upon joining Wedge Antilles's Wraith Squadron.
